exports[`card builders (hover-pipeline.tsx) > buildSinkCard: sink shows accepted modes + compatibility + DDL/INSERT 1`] = `
"**JdbcSink** ┬Ě _Sink_

Writes to a relational database via JDBC.

| column | type |
|---|---|
| \`order_id\` | \`BIGINT\` |
| \`amount\` | \`DECIMAL(10, 2)\` |
| \`order_time\` | \`TIMESTAMP(3)\` |

Accepts changelog modes: append-only, retract, upsert
Upstream mode \`append-only\` ÔÇö Ôťô compatible

\`\`\`sql
CREATE TABLE \`orders_filtered\` (
  \`order_id\` BIGINT,
  \`amount\` DECIMAL(10, 2),
  \`order_time\` TIMESTAMP(3),
  PRIMARY KEY (\`order_id\`) NOT ENFORCED
) WITH (
  'connector' = 'jdbc',
  'table-name' = 'orders_filtered',
  'url' = 'jdbc:postgresql://db:5432/app'
);

INSERT INTO \`orders_filtered\`
SELECT * FROM \`orders\` WHERE amount > 0;
\`\`\`

ÔČć upstream: \`Filter\` ┬Ě ÔČç downstream: ÔÇö"
`;

exports[`card builders (hover-pipeline.tsx) > buildTagCard: source shows schema + changelog + DDL + neighbors 1`] = `
"**KafkaSource** ┬Ě _Source_

Reads from an Apache Kafka topic.

| column | type |
|---|---|
| \`order_id\` | \`BIGINT\` |
| \`amount\` | \`DECIMAL(10, 2)\` |
| \`order_time\` | \`TIMESTAMP(3)\` |

Changelog mode: **append-only**

\`\`\`sql
CREATE TABLE \`orders\` (
  \`order_id\` BIGINT,
  \`amount\` DECIMAL(10, 2),
  \`order_time\` TIMESTAMP(3)
) WITH (
  'connector' = 'kafka',
  'format' = 'json',
  'properties.bootstrap.servers' = 'kafka:9092',
  'scan.startup.mode' = 'earliest-offset',
  'topic' = 'orders'
);
\`\`\`

ÔČć upstream: ÔÇö ┬Ě ÔČç downstream: \`Filter\`"
`;

